<font color="#FF0000">REPLY TO DOC SPATZ</font><br>
<tt>Sat May 31 14:22:59 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Doc Spatz:<br><br>
I am not angry with you.<br><br>
I feel that we have a kind of style problem here.<br><br>
I am fully aware of Nurse Ratchet's point of view, having been on this site since Nov. 96. If you will read my posts here carefully, word for word, exactly word for word, you will see that I have not been drawn into a web of deception.<br>
As a matter of fact, I was just being friendly. There is nothing wrong with that.<br><br>
I said:<br><br>
&gt;&quot;Don't be too hasty with the diploma yet!&quot;&lt;<br><br>
and..<br><br>
&gt;&quot;Be patient with me, and I will listen, and though I may not always agree, I will give you a fair shake.&quot;&lt;<br><br>
The next thing I see is the equivalent of a thermonuclear explosion and shock wave careening across the internet.<br><br>
KABOOM!<br><br>
Right after that I felt like I was tackled by the entire line of the Green Bay Packers.<br><br>
SQUISH!<br><br>
My self esteem went to hell, and I began to feel angry, and popped you one between the eyes.<br><br>
KAPOW!<br><br>
Now, let's make a distinction here. <br><br>
Nurse Ratchet is and will always be Nurse Ratchet. We all have some feelings about his style and personal philosophy.<br>
You, in particular, feel strongly about his presence. That's OK because Nurse Ratchet is a big boy and can take care of himself. I notice he has not taken you up on your challenge. You made some really good points.<br><br>
My posts, on the other hand, are a bit touchy with me. It is far better to respond to me separately about their content and whatever concerns or alternative thoughts you may have to offer, in the interest of constructivism, and not intermingle that process with your zeal about Nurse Ratchet.<br><br>
In that way, you can kick the pants off Nurse Ratchet, communicate your thoughts to me, I won't get triggered and regress into a protective and agressive PTSD fog, and we can keep our relationship on an even keel, where it really belongs.<br><br>
OK? :)<br><br>
(Let's take this off line if I am not clear. In fact, I will call you so we can speak personally, if that is what it will take. &lt;g&gt;)<br><br>
Art<br><br>
